; Required header — removing or renaming this will break the file.

50:2:combos/tier1.ogg:%combo% click combo! Your output is now %multiplier%x per press!
75:4:combos/tier2.ogg:%combo% click combo! You're hitting your stride! %multiplier%x per press!
100:6:combos/tier3.ogg:%combo% click combo! Incredible baking! %multiplier%x per press!
125:8:combos/tier4.ogg:%combo% click combo! Legendary! Your cookies are flying out of the oven at %multiplier%x per press!
150:10:combos/tier5.ogg:%combo% click combo! Unstoppable! The oven can barely keep up at %multiplier%x per press!
175:12:combos/tier6.ogg:%combo% click combo! Cookie frenzy! You're breaking every baking record at %multiplier%x per press!
200:14:combos/tier7.ogg:%combo% click combo! Transcendent! The cookies are practically baking themselves at %multiplier%x per press!
225:16:combos/tier8.ogg:%combo% click combo! Cookie Singularity! Reality itself bends to your will at %multiplier%x per press!
